SCHEMA: net/delta.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.net.delta
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic delta artifact metadata for tick ranges.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record net_delta
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - delta_id: id
    - tick_from: u64
    - tick_to: u64
    - shard_id: text
    - payload_ref: text
    - delta_hash: hash64
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- tick_to >= tick_from
- delta_hash must identify canonical delta payload bytes.
